# Cloudflare Pages redirects — kept only for the SPA fallback. Pages
# `_redirects` doesn't support cross-origin proxying, so the API
# proxy lives as a Pages Function:
#   /api/rt/<feed>/<endpoint>  →  functions/api/rt/[feed]/[[endpoint]].js
# The Function reads the upstream URL from feeds.json.
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# SPA fallback for client-side routing (SvelteKit outputs index.html
# from adapter-static). Must be last.
/*                         /index.html                                200
